properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS Metro North West trackwork - CHATSWOOD Railway Street between Day Street AND Help Street
properties.otherAdvice:
Special event clearways will be in effect on the eastern side of Railway St between Day St and Help St to facilitate rail replacement bus operations for Sydney Metro trackwork. No-stopping zones will also be in place on the western side of Railway St between Help St and Brown St during this time. 

Special event clearways are strict no-parking zones and also apply to local residents and Mobility Scheme Parking Permit holders. Vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
properties.displayName: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS Metro North West trackwork

properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS Metro North West trackwork - CHATSWOOD Brown Street between Railway Street AND Pacific Highway
properties.otherAdvice:

No-stopping zones will also be in place on the western side of Railway St between Help St and Brown St during this time. 

Special event clearways are strict no-parking zones and also apply to local residents and Mobility Scheme Parking Permit holders. Vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
properties.displayName: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS Metro North West trackwork

properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - SYDNEY CBD Clarence Street between Margaret Street AND Market Street, Sydney
properties.otherAdvice:
Special event clearways will be in effect on both sides of Clarence St between Margaret St and Market St to facilitate construction work on Carrington St for the Bus Priority Infrastructure Program as well as rail replacement bus operations for Sydney Trains trackwork.

Clearways are strict no-parking zones and also apply to local residents and Mobility Scheme Parking Permit holders. Vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
